The paper discusses the quality of experience (QoE) in mobile computing systems, which involves network services and mobile devices. This topic is closely related to computer networks (cs.NI) as well as human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also mentions cognitive and behavioral states, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the quality of service (QoS), which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT).
